Package: debconf-translator
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1
Description: GTK4 tool for managing Debconf template translations
 Debconf Translation Manager helps translators work with Debian package
 configuration dialogs (debconf templates). Features include a dashboard
 with translation statistics, built-in PO editor, review board tracking,
 and BTS submission tools.
